{"tid":863775,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有乘客由鑽石山站前往九龍塘站花了40分鐘","createTime":"2018-10-16T00:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T01:35:06.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d0bffe5eb9edbd83378367ee86d4afde190232","tid":863775,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:32:49.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，由於信號系統故障，荃灣綫、港島綫及觀塘綫三條綫，列車要慢駛，目前大約要12至15分鐘一班。因應觀塘綫及港島綫事故，將軍澳綫亦要額外行車時間，北角站往返康城站，每12分鐘一班；北角站往返寶琳站每6分鐘一班。港鐵呼籲乘客為行程預留充裕時間。港鐵代表稍後會在青衣站見記者，交代信號系統故障原因。<br />\n<br />\n在九龍塘站，港鐵有廣播指，三條路綫列車因信號系統故障要慢駛，由於觀塘綫月台迫滿候車乘客，職員要分批讓乘客落月台。有由鑽石山前往荃灣西的市民說，單是前往九龍塘站，就已花了40分鐘，由於提早出門，暫時不擔心會遲到。有乘客表示，多條路綫列車同時受阻，情況較罕見。"},{"pid":"998e83eb7590a188a34dba382c95165d721d8ad6","tid":863775,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:33:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1035703&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1035703%26csid%3D261_341&d=MG1RhEaUUK%2FKh99n64VWFJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=142b292f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1035703&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"7e1bf531599287b9cd2f525917d3d5616e00d8df","tid":863775,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:33:47.000Z","msg":"體諒下啦 香港要發展"},{"pid":"48b9fe5e5e2fc73ee4d31bf7da5ae9cb0e1e03a8","tid":863775,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:34:00.000Z","msg":"行老龍一樣有出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee1671fc172da2167440cc80c1ff6d89a09d74c","tid":863775,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T00:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831b07fceee24eed2562e3389dd7d968c305a242","tid":863775,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"c